00:02:34.239 --> 00:02:37.120
Truly, it's changed our lives.

00:02:37.120 --> 00:02:39.109
This has changed our lives.

00:02:39.109 --> 00:02:43.386
Seeing people in public and seeing people at church, they come from everywhere.

00:02:43.386 --> 00:02:46.299
