00:03:48.623 --> 00:03:49.775
Prayer changes things.

00:03:49.775 --> 00:03:51.013
That's who we are.

00:03:51.013 --> 00:03:54.777
So we jumped in the boat with a bunch of prayer warriors.

00:03:54.777 --> 00:03:57.919
Candace and Billye Brim and their daughter.

00:03:57.919 --> 00:04:00.948
They're some of the greatest prayer warriors of this generation.

00:04:00.948 --> 00:04:05.280
