00:04:11.519 --> 00:04:20.648
So, and the other part of our vein of what God's called us to do is the prophetic and hearing and seeing watchmen and doing things that the Lord's called us to do.

00:04:20.648 --> 00:04:25.600
So, we find ground like that and we sow into it.

00:04:25.600 --> 00:04:32.400
We sow into prayer warrior ground, covering of prayer, because when you're in this, we've dealt with a lot of spiritual warfare.

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:34.240
We sow into all the grounds.

00:04:34.240 --> 00:04:38.410
Yeah, we sow into all the ground, it's just where we feel like we need it.

00:04:38.410 --> 00:04:43.030
Sometimes you feel like you're lacking more in one area when we pray about where to sow.

00:04:43.040 --> 00:04:44.760
But it is specific.

00:04:44.760 --> 00:04:48.080
We are strategic in where we sow.

00:04:48.720 --> 00:05:04.479
Because it may be that we're going through certain things that are more than others on that day, and we say, 'I feel like we should give x amount of dollars to this ministry because it could be like prayer warrior ground.

00:05:04.479 --> 00:05:07.326
' It's like I saw Sister Billye and them.

00:05:07.326 --> 00:05:10.920
They're like Vikings in the spirit realm.

00:05:10.920 --> 00:05:12.200
They're like, 'Where's the devil?

00:05:12.200 --> 00:05:13.531
' You know, you go after the devil.

00:05:13.531 --> 00:05:17.067
You know, it's like these people have that authority.

00:05:17.067 --> 00:05:30.208
They walk in the authority, talking about the authority of the believer and taking your rights according to Ephesians and exercising that, and you can feel it when you sow into their ground.

00:05:30.208 --> 00:05:32.960
You feel that covering.

00:05:33.344 --> 00:05:34.880
It's amazing, isn't it?

00:05:34.880 --> 00:05:44.320
So then you go, 'Okay, well, I've got that base covered, but I need a little bit of because God's called us into the healing ministry.

00:05:44.320 --> 00:05:52.080
' So we find a healing ministry and we're like, 'Who's a healing ministry that we really can trust, that you know that there's fruit behind their ministry?

00:05:52.080 --> 00:05:53.314
' And that's Billy Burke.

00:05:53.314 --> 00:05:58.240
So we say, 'Well, let's sow a little seed into Billy Burke's ministry.

00:05:58.240 --> 00:06:07.279
' So as you give into that, there's a blessing that comes from that, and I believe that covering comes over you.

00:06:07.279 --> 00:06:13.760
And it's like people go, 'Brandon, I have a problem with hearing the voice of God.

00:06:13.760 --> 00:06:18.971
' Well, if I hear the voice of God and you have a problem with that, I sow into what?

00:06:18.971 --> 00:06:26.853
I sow by faith into the prophetic, and I say, 'Here's seed into the prophetic ministry.

00:06:26.853 --> 00:06:43.280
' And I'm sowing this by faith that my ears are going to become more attuned, the prophetic antenna, hearing the voice of the Father, because he said in his word that we would hear his voice, and a stranger's voice we wouldn't follow.

00:06:43.280 --> 00:06:51.663
And as I sow, I sow intentionally into that, praying for the covering of that to come on me.

00:06:51.663 --> 00:07:03.904
I say, 'Lord, I thank you that as I sow into the prophetic, Father, I thank you, Lord, that that's coming on me and my household because blessings come down.

00:07:03.904 --> 00:07:18.160
' And I've noticed if you need wisdom in scripture, I sow into scholar ground, which is people who are real educated and teachers of the gospel that teach.

00:07:18.160 --> 00:07:26.288
Some ministries have a gift of teaching, and you go there and you listen to them and you go, 'Man, I got a lot out of that.

00:07:26.288 --> 00:07:28.850
That was a lot of rhema word.

00:07:28.850 --> 00:07:35.900
' Like Brother Hagin when he was on the earth, he was a teacher but he walked in the prophetic also.

00:07:35.900 --> 00:07:44.983
So, in the past when he was here on the earth—now he's not here no more—but I would sow into him directly, whatever you could give into that or whatever.

00:07:44.983 --> 00:07:48.902
You get what I'm saying, y'all.

00:07:50.319 --> 00:07:53.599
Wherever you have a need, you sow a seed.

00:07:53.599 --> 00:07:58.879
If I need covering of prayer, I sow into prayer.

00:07:58.879 --> 00:08:01.652
If you feel like you're under spiritual attack, does it make sense?

00:08:01.652 --> 00:08:04.089
Prayer ministries, prayer things like that, you sow into that.

00:08:04.089 --> 00:08:09.440
