00:08:09.440 --> 00:08:12.140
If I need healing, I sow into healing ministries.

00:08:12.140 --> 00:08:19.360
If I sow into financial, I look at the people who are bringing in a lot of souls.

00:08:19.360 --> 00:08:21.246
Who's bringing in the harvest?

00:08:21.246 --> 00:08:25.805
So I sow into—for 'he that wins souls is wise.

00:08:25.805 --> 00:08:32.151
' So, I see people's ministries that have a financial blessing on them that bring in a lot of souls.

00:08:32.151 --> 00:08:34.800
Like Billy Graham was one when he was alive, okay?

00:08:34.800 --> 00:08:36.240
