00:08:51.680 --> 00:08:53.000
I just go, 'You know what?

00:08:53.000 --> 00:08:54.377
Let's just stay on course.

00:08:54.377 --> 00:08:57.030
' Don't go over here and way over there.

00:08:57.610 --> 00:09:01.450
