00:09:01.450 --> 00:09:04.700
There's a lot of weird stuff out there, and I go, 'You know what?

00:09:04.700 --> 00:09:08.779
If they got people born again and they turn people to Jesus, I'm on your side.

00:09:08.779 --> 00:09:12.240
' Let's just stay on the side of the body of Christ and be all for each other and pray for each other.

00:09:13.264 --> 00:09:17.057
Now, I've got a lot of haters, but you know what?

00:09:17.057 --> 00:09:18.800
I look at them and say, 'We pray for them.

00:09:18.800 --> 00:09:21.440
' They make videos of me, and I say, 'Listen, we're going to love on them anyway.

00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:27.330
' It doesn't matter what people say about you; it's what you allow inside, how you feel about them.

00:09:27.750 --> 00:09:32.907
I'm not going to get bitter; I refuse to walk out of love.

00:09:32.907 --> 00:09:39.886
You may not agree with what I say, but the Bible says, 'Touch not mine anointed, and do my prophets no harm.

00:09:39.886 --> 00:09:46.640
' Don't touch people with your mouth, regardless of what they say about you, what they feel about you, or how they act.

00:09:46.640 --> 00:09:47.707
