00:09:47.707 --> 00:09:50.666
My job is to automatically walk in love.

00:09:50.666 --> 00:09:56.994
They can call me a false prophet, they can call me all these things, but my foundation is to say, 'You know what, brother?

00:09:56.994 --> 00:09:57.886
We're praying for you.

00:09:57.886 --> 00:09:59.060
We pray for your marriage.

00:09:59.060 --> 00:10:00.360
We pray for your wife.

00:10:00.360 --> 00:10:04.399
