00:10:04.399 --> 00:10:11.063
' Regardless of what you feel about me, if I'm not going to be buddies with you, that's fine, but I'm going to pray for you instead.

00:10:11.474 --> 00:10:20.560
It's important that we always, no matter how much people persecute the body of Christ—I catch it all from all kinds of people.

00:10:20.560 --> 00:10:25.262
The world hates me, and a lot of Christians do, but you know what?

00:10:25.262 --> 00:10:29.340
I choose to walk in love because love takes no account of a suffered wrong.

00:10:29.340 --> 00:10:31.520
You may say, 'Well, he doesn't hear God at all.

00:10:31.520 --> 00:10:32.594
He doesn't say all these things.

00:10:32.594 --> 00:10:32.869
' Whatever.

00:10:32.869 --> 00:10:35.360
I just keep on doing what God has called me to do.

00:10:35.360 --> 00:10:36.880
It's like I talked to somebody on the phone.

00:10:36.880 --> 00:10:43.519
They said, 'An apple doesn't have to announce that it's an apple.

00:10:46.027 --> 00:10:48.256
An orange doesn't have to announce it's an orange.

00:10:49.152 --> 00:10:53.896
They automatically display who they are, and they taste of what they're supposed to be.

00:10:53.896 --> 00:10:59.867
' So, a prophetic ministry is going to be a prophetic ministry, and you're going to taste and see it.

00:10:59.867 --> 00:11:03.462
