00:11:03.462 --> 00:11:03.645
I'm a prophet.

00:11:04.011 --> 00:11:04.194
I'm a prophet.

00:11:04.194 --> 00:11:06.377
' Because if they're always going around saying, 'I'm Prophet so-and-so.

00:11:06.548 --> 00:11:10.930
I'm Prophet this, Prophet that,' you don't have to announce it.

00:11:10.930 --> 00:11:18.286
Your fruit of who you are in your ministry is automatically going to display when you show up, because you carry that anointing.

00:11:21.429 --> 00:11:22.800
You're a carrier of it.

00:11:22.800 --> 00:11:23.839
Aren't you right, baby?

00:11:24.320 --> 00:11:29.120
And it's like Billy Burke doesn't have to come around and tell everybody, 'I'm a healing evangelist.

00:11:29.120 --> 00:11:30.240
Glory to God.

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:35.040
' You see the fruit of who he is when he walks in and comes up on the platform.

00:11:35.040 --> 00:11:35.440
Bam!

00:11:35.440 --> 00:11:43.279
The atmosphere changes, and people's lives are getting changed and they're getting healed, and you can see the authenticity.

00:11:43.279 --> 00:11:52.610
The Holy Spirit leads and guides you to know and to see visibly the ones who are authentic versus those who are pretenders.

00:11:52.610 --> 00:11:56.431
I don't have to tell you I'm an orange if I'm an orange.

00:11:57.680 --> 00:11:59.600
