00:11:59.600 --> 00:12:12.079
And there are a lot of people who try to tell you and convince you that they're an apple when they're not an apple—they're a plum, and you're going, 'That doesn't line up right,' because signs will follow them that believe.

00:12:12.079 --> 00:12:15.021
Signs follow the anointing that's on your life.

00:12:15.021 --> 00:12:19.670
