00:12:19.670 --> 00:12:20.257
I don't care.

00:12:20.257 --> 00:12:21.580
I'm just going to keep doing it.

00:12:21.580 --> 00:12:26.560
And if the Lord corrects me and says, 'Brandon, you're off,' then I'm going to say, 'Okay, forgive me, Lord, but I want to help people.

00:12:26.560 --> 00:12:29.840
