00:12:34.680 --> 00:12:36.533
' Just like Pastor Chip is always talking.

00:12:36.533 --> 00:12:40.880
Brother Hagin told him, 'Chip, if you want to stay on target...

00:12:40.880 --> 00:12:43.759
' How to sow into good ground...

00:12:43.759 --> 00:13:05.240
Brother Hagin told our pastor, Pastor Chip, when we go to our church there, he said, 'If you don't ever want to get off in life and get off on the wrong road, this is the main key that you need to focus on: in all that you do, in word and in deed, do all to the glory of God, and you'll not get off track.

00:13:05.240 --> 00:13:11.173
' Everything I do, I'm doing in word and in deed; I do all for the glory of God.

00:13:11.173 --> 00:13:16.915
So if they don't agree with what you're doing and they want to throw eggs at you, say, 'I'm just doing all to the glory of God.

00:13:16.915 --> 00:13:18.860
I'm not doing this for me, brother.

00:13:18.860 --> 00:13:20.630
I'm doing all to the glory of God.

00:13:20.630 --> 00:13:25.490
' He said, 'If I be lifted up, I'll draw all men unto me.

00:13:25.490 --> 00:13:29.320
' Because, like Billy Burke said, it's 'to attract, to deflect.

00:13:29.320 --> 00:13:35.188
