00:13:35.188 --> 00:13:39.173
And the more it grows, we give all the glory to God.

00:13:39.173 --> 00:13:43.999
And when you do that, you stay on track because you're giving all glory to Him.

00:13:43.999 --> 00:13:45.573
It's all glory to You, Lord.

00:13:47.690 --> 00:13:53.973
We give all the glory to Jesus and tell of His love.

00:13:56.880 --> 00:14:01.360
We give all of the glory to Jesus.

00:14:01.360 --> 00:14:03.920
That's where it's at.

00:14:03.920 --> 00:14:06.651
I feel like people need to hear this.

00:14:06.651 --> 00:14:16.340
