00:14:56.928 --> 00:14:58.720
There's something wrong.

00:14:58.720 --> 00:15:01.120
' Sow somewhere else.

00:15:01.120 --> 00:15:02.080
Poof!

00:15:05.813 --> 00:15:13.150
I mean seriously, because you go, 'There's something off with this ground,' and you know because the ground where you're sowing will produce.

00:15:13.150 --> 00:15:15.519
So we automatically test it.

00:15:15.519 --> 00:15:19.760
