00:16:42.994 --> 00:16:44.292
We didn't even know it.

00:16:44.897 --> 00:16:46.720
It was a light up, and she put it over the door.

00:16:56.959 --> 00:16:57.142
It was just a little light up sign that said, "Prayer changes things.

00:17:09.520 --> 00:17:09.954
" And she would go in there with whoever the girl was that she started the ministry with, her friend, her sister or cousin or something like that, right?

