00:38:12.000 --> 00:38:13.149
Does that make sense?

00:38:13.149 --> 00:38:24.960
If my kids are in the youth group and the youth leader is not good, or your children's church pastor or whatever, and your kids aren't growing spiritually or they're not changing, look and evaluate spiritually of where you are.

00:38:37.383 --> 00:38:37.691
And I'm not telling you it's not the pastor's fault on everything, you know what I'm saying?

00:38:38.190 --> 00:38:38.760
You have to evaluate you.

00:38:38.760 --> 00:38:40.675
What are you doing to grow yourself spiritually?

00:38:40.675 --> 00:38:42.133
Are you getting something from there?

00:38:44.800 --> 00:38:47.307
And if God has called you there to help out there or whatever, have you done what He's called you to do?

00:38:47.307 --> 00:38:48.409
Have you grown?

00:38:48.409 --> 00:38:57.809
If you're not going from glory to glory and you're at a church and you go, "You know, they don't believe in the baptism of the Holy Ghost," for one, I'd be out of there.

00:38:57.809 --> 00:39:11.876
If they don't believe in the baptism of the Holy Ghost, if they don't believe in divine healing and they'll lay hands on you, it's like I heard one preacher say, "You'll believe in healing whenever you're desperate and you have stage four cancer.

00:39:19.314 --> 00:39:19.611
" That's what Billy Burke said.

00:39:19.611 --> 00:39:24.222
He goes, "Yeah, told me, 'I don't believe God can heal.

00:39:24.222 --> 00:39:25.691
' Well, you're not sick enough.

00:39:25.691 --> 00:39:30.663
" If you're overcoming something really bad, you're going to believe something desperate.

00:39:38.459 --> 00:39:38.909
You'll believe.

00:39:38.909 --> 00:39:42.221
But what kind of cart are you attaching your horses to?

00:39:44.1000 --> 00:39:50.600
I don't want to attach to people that don't believe in divine healing, that don't believe in laying hands on the sick.

00:40:03.691 --> 00:40:04.137
And if I'm overcoming something, they're going, "You know, sometimes God does and sometimes He doesn't, brother.

00:40:18.960 --> 00:40:19.480
It might be your time to go home.

00:40:22.000 --> 00:40:22.263
" I don't want that in my corner.

00:40:35.360 --> 00:40:35.640
I want somebody to go there and say, "I believe God with you, and I'm standing with you that you're healed by the stripes of Jesus, and you're going to get healed," and try to speak life into me.

00:40:45.230 --> 00:40:45.520
And believes in praying in tongues.

00:40:45.520 --> 00:40:58.900
Believes in teaching my kids to live a holy lifestyle and that they've got what it takes to make it in this world in school, and cast out devils if you've got a devil or whatever.

00:40:58.900 --> 00:40:59.920
Not, "Well, you know what?

00:41:00.032 --> 00:41:01.540
I don't really believe that you can have a devil.

00:41:01.540 --> 00:41:08.880
" No, I'm telling you, I've seen Christians flat out say they're born again, growling and acting crazy with a demonic spirit attached to their soulish realm.

00:41:08.880 --> 00:41:11.350
No, it's not attached to their spirit.

00:41:11.350 --> 00:41:17.280
But I'm telling you, I've seen demonic attachments onto folks that are born-again believers, and they are growling, acting crazy, and manifested right there.

00:41:17.280 --> 00:41:24.559
And you've got to get them free because it's coming out of the mind, will, and the emotions.

00:41:24.559 --> 00:41:28.411
Your spirit is renewed, and all that happens with your spirit, right?

00:41:36.256 --> 00:41:36.623
But your body has stuff that has attachments.

00:41:36.623 --> 00:41:37.919
Alcohol addiction, pornography...

00:41:38.200 --> 00:41:45.029
you open a door for the devil to come in to kill, steal, and destroy you, and you get attachments.

00:41:51.620 --> 00:41:51.890
And I call them little—they're little boogeymen that go lay on your shoulder, and you've got to get free from that stuff.

00:41:55.359 --> 00:42:02.091
And if you read Pigs in the Parlor and these other books, they'll help you.

00:42:02.457 --> 00:42:04.640
But I don't get into the demonic stuff.

00:42:10.116 --> 00:42:10.444
I don't give them any place.

00:42:10.444 --> 00:42:12.857
I don't even talk about the demonic.

00:42:33.577 --> 00:42:34.046
But there's some people that need to know when it comes to addictions through pornography, through drugs, alcohol, any kind of perversion, the devil will, if you open the door, he's going to set up shop in your life.

00:42:40.309 --> 00:42:40.579
If you don't fill yourself up, they come back more.

00:42:40.579 --> 00:42:42.940
They come and try to torment your mind.

00:42:42.940 --> 00:42:50.300
They try to do all, and you've got to get your mind renewed in this Word.

00:42:50.300 --> 00:42:55.440
You cannot just pray in the spirit over demonic stuff and think you're going to get freedom.

00:42:55.440 --> 00:42:57.119
The Bible is the sword.

00:42:57.119 --> 00:43:01.500
You've got to speak this sword out of your mouth and cut that devil.

00:43:01.500 --> 00:43:02.650
But it's the truth.

00:43:12.708 --> 00:43:12.982
You know, the Bible says you know the truth and the truth will set you free.

00:43:14.859 --> 00:43:21.147
The only freedom and the truth, the only thing that's ever going to set you free is knowing this truth: the truth of the Word of God.

00:43:28.596 --> 00:43:30.827
The Word of God inside of your mouth is sharper than any two-edged sword, and it goes out of your mouth, and true freedom comes from the Word and cuts that devil.

00:43:30.827 --> 00:43:34.629
But if you're just praying in the spirit—"God, Jesus, thank you, Lord.

00:43:34.629 --> 00:43:45.253
Father, I just thank you, Lord"—it says, "If ye abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done unto you.

00:43:47.005 --> 00:43:49.093
" But you have to get the Word abiding in you and His words remaining.

00:43:49.093 --> 00:43:59.760
"If ye abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:43:59.760 --> 00:44:05.059
" So you have to get this Word inside of you speaking.

00:44:07.359 --> 00:44:07.656
We are speaking spirits.

00:44:07.656 --> 00:44:13.737
We are speaking forth this Word out of our mouth, and that's what changes you.

00:44:25.080 --> 00:44:25.440
And the devil knows when you know the truth.

00:44:25.440 --> 00:44:32.192
The devil knows when you know who you are, instead of saying verses of "Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star, how I wonder what you are.

00:44:32.960 --> 00:44:39.509
" You can say a word and quote scripture, and I can read it one time: "Devil, this is what the Bible says.

00:44:41.600 --> 00:44:48.789
" He knows the Word better than you do, but it's the truth that you know inside of you, that you have a Rhema word on the inside of you that's going to set you free.

00:44:48.789 --> 00:44:58.027
Like 2 Timothy 1:7: "God has not given me a spirit of fear, but of power and of love and of a sound mind.

00:44:58.027 --> 00:45:05.291
" Getting that Word down inside of your heart, and that's how you'll know the truth and the truth will set you free.

00:45:05.291 --> 00:45:06.859
I've seen devil-casting-out services.

00:45:06.859 --> 00:45:12.853
There's all this stuff, and they go through the healing line, but they fall out, laid out.

00:45:12.853 --> 00:45:16.446
They have a courtesy fall or whatever, and they get out.

00:45:24.859 --> 00:45:25.280
But as Diana said, "I don't want to fall just to fall.

00:45:25.280 --> 00:45:27.470
I want to get up different.

00:45:27.470 --> 00:45:28.149
I want impartation.

00:45:32.000 --> 00:45:32.900
" But the only thing that's truly going to give you impartation is the Word, understanding the Word of God.

00:45:34.280 --> 00:45:40.240
And I'm telling you, when you open the door for sin, you open the door for the devil.

00:45:40.240 --> 00:45:42.686
He's going to come right in.

00:45:42.686 --> 00:45:48.079
But this is the only thing that's going to keep you free.

00:45:48.079 --> 00:45:54.160
And that's just like they say, the Word works if you work it.

00:46:03.100 --> 00:46:03.290
And when you find scripture that pertains to you, that's something you're believing for.

00:46:03.290 --> 00:46:15.110
Another thing that we do is we write it down on sticky notes and we put it on the mirror or maybe under your visor of your car.

00:46:27.440 --> 00:46:27.680
I read one story about this man who was trying to recover from smoking cigarettes, and he had a scripture that he spoke every time that pertained to smoking cigarettes.

00:46:27.680 --> 00:46:36.571
He would flip his visor down and he had it written down on a little sticky, and every time he had the thought about smoking a cigarette, he would quote that scripture.

00:46:38.844 --> 00:46:43.919
And that's how it gets down inside of you.

00:46:53.750 --> 00:46:54.000
But it is only the truth that you know that will set you free.

00:46:54.000 --> 00:46:55.929
It's not just reading it once.

00:46:55.929 --> 00:47:02.980
Faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God over and over again.

00:47:07.051 --> 00:47:12.199
And I know that you will know the truth, and the truth will make you free and set you free.

00:47:13.460 --> 00:47:21.154
And I believe that's why so many people in the body of Christ live so bound with all these addictions.

00:47:21.154 --> 00:47:24.408
We're not made to live bound.

00:47:24.408 --> 00:47:27.670
God made us to have an abundant life, to the full, until it overflows.

00:47:38.979 --> 00:47:39.309
And if you're not living abundantly in finances, health, prosperity, and mental clarity, you have to go back and check your word gauge.

00:47:39.309 --> 00:47:41.236
Where is my word level?

00:47:41.236 --> 00:47:42.889
Is it the pastor's fault?

00:47:42.889 --> 00:47:44.520
Well, that's Pastor Chip's fault.

00:47:44.520 --> 00:47:49.893
It's probably Pastor T's fault; she didn't preach a good enough word this week.

00:47:49.893 --> 00:47:51.730
No, it's not their fault.

00:47:51.730 --> 00:47:55.839
It's not the fault of the people you go to.

00:47:55.839 --> 00:47:57.074
It's your fault.

00:47:57.074 --> 00:48:03.556
You have 24 hours in a day, seven days a week, just like I do.

00:48:03.556 --> 00:48:08.426
We all have the opportunity to turn on something on YouTube or whatever—a word, a preaching sermon.

00:48:08.426 --> 00:48:17.920
We listen to Kenneth Hagin a lot and listen to his old stuff—find stuff clear back in the '80s and munch on that and go, 'Was that good?

00:48:17.920 --> 00:48:18.789
It's okay.

00:48:18.789 --> 00:48:19.611
Next one.

00:48:19.611 --> 00:48:22.903
' You know, and go, 'Boy, that was good.

00:48:22.903 --> 00:48:23.909
Let's find it.

00:48:23.909 --> 00:48:25.303
Let's keep listening to it.

00:48:25.303 --> 00:48:30.400
' There's one that I told her, 'We've got to go over it again and again.

00:48:30.400 --> 00:48:32.448
' I listened to one this week.

00:48:32.448 --> 00:48:35.707
