00:49:20.069 --> 00:49:31.736
I don't know, when you hear somebody talking—I don't like performance, and I'm not saying Brother Hagin ever was performance, but there are certain sermons when you listen to people where you go, 'I don't want performance.

00:49:35.520 --> 00:49:35.829
