00:54:51.200 --> 00:54:53.199
That's God's economy, and I'm going to participate in God's economy.

00:54:53.199 --> 00:55:02.271
That's what He said about me: I am what He says I am, I will have what He said I could have, and I will do what the Bible says I can do.

